{"title":"元胞自动机","uid":"9ab102218820989ff828dc66fb438e13","slug":"元胞自动机","date":"2021-07-30T07:03:17.000Z","updated":"2021-07-30T08:41:16.138Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/元胞自动机.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/theme/2021730_1.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"元胞自动机\"><a href=\"#元胞自动机\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"元胞自动机\"></a>元胞自动机</h1><p><b>元胞自动机的构成：</b>原版自动机由<strong>元胞、元胞空间、元胞邻居和元胞规则</strong>四部分组成；</p>\n<p><b>元胞状态：</b>在最简单的情况下，元胞有两种可能状态；较复杂情况下，具有多种状态，元胞的状态都按照元胞自动机的动力规则不断更新；</p>\n<p><b>邻居：</b>某一元胞状态更新是所要搜索的空间域就是该元胞的邻居；常见有夫诺伊曼型、Moor型以及扩展Moor型等；</p>\n<p><b>边界条件：</b>理论上，元胞空间是无限的，实际应用中无法达到这一理想条件，为了给元胞空间边界上的元胞拥有规则所需的邻居，就需要构造出一些虚拟的邻居；常见的边界条件类型有：<strong>固定型、周期型、绝热型和映射型</strong>这四种；</p>\n<p><b>规则：</b>根据元胞当前状态以及邻居状态来决定下一时刻该元胞状态；</p>\n<p><b>元胞自动机的应用：</b>元胞自动机模型可以用来<strong>模拟交通流、火灾蔓延情况、高速收费站交通情况</strong>，有利于我们更好地改善交通状况，更好地控制火灾蔓延，合理地设置收费站的数量等</p>\n<p><strong>实例：</strong>当邻居数值之和为偶数那么元胞的下一状态为0，如果和为奇数则下一状态为1</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">import numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nn &#x3D; 200\nSe &#x3D; np.zeros([n,n])\nz &#x3D; np.zeros([n,n])\n# 设置一些初始值\nSe[int(n&#x2F;2-2):int(n&#x2F;2+2),int(n&#x2F;2-2):int(n&#x2F;2+2)] &#x3D; 1\n# 边界条件\nSd &#x3D; np.zeros([n+2,n+2])\nwhile True:\n    Sd[1:n+1,1:n+1] &#x3D; Se\n    Sum &#x3D; Sd[0:n,1:n+1] + Sd[2:n+2,1:n+1] + Sd[1:n+1,0:n] + Sd[1:n+1,2:n+2]\n    Se &#x3D; Sum%2</code></pre>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>澳洲火灾</strong></p>\n<p>经典的森林火灾元胞自动机模型是由Drossel和Schwabl在1992年提出的。森林火灾元胞自动机模型定义在正方形网格上，元胞有三种状态：树、火和空地</p>\n<p>它的规则为：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>树<svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"2.324ex\" height=\"1.843ex\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.338ex;\" viewBox=\"0 -647.8 1000.5 793.3\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-labelledby=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\n<title id=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\\Rightarrow</title>\n<defs aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-21D2\" d=\"M580 514Q580 525 596 525Q601 525 604 525T609 525T613 524T615 523T617 520T619 517T622 512Q659 438 720 381T831 300T927 263Q944 258 944 250T935 239T898 228T840 204Q696 134 622 -12Q618 -21 615 -22T600 -24Q580 -24 580 -17Q580 -13 585 0Q620 69 671 123L681 133H70Q56 140 56 153Q56 168 72 173H725L735 181Q774 211 852 250Q851 251 834 259T789 283T735 319L725 327H72Q56 332 56 347Q56 360 70 367H681L671 377Q638 412 609 458T580 514Z\"></path>\n</defs>\n<g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-21D2\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use>\n</g>\n</svg>火(火能够燃烧树)</li>\n<li>闪电<svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"2.324ex\" height=\"1.843ex\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.338ex;\" viewBox=\"0 -647.8 1000.5 793.3\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-labelledby=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\n<title id=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\\Rightarrow</title>\n<defs aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-21D2\" d=\"M580 514Q580 525 596 525Q601 525 604 525T609 525T613 524T615 523T617 520T619 517T622 512Q659 438 720 381T831 300T927 263Q944 258 944 250T935 239T898 228T840 204Q696 134 622 -12Q618 -21 615 -22T600 -24Q580 -24 580 -17Q580 -13 585 0Q620 69 671 123L681 133H70Q56 140 56 153Q56 168 72 173H725L735 181Q774 211 852 250Q851 251 834 259T789 283T735 319L725 327H72Q56 332 56 347Q56 360 70 367H681L671 377Q638 412 609 458T580 514Z\"></path>\n</defs>\n<g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-21D2\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use>\n</g>\n</svg>火(闪电劈中树引发火)</li>\n<li>火<svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"2.324ex\" height=\"1.843ex\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.338ex;\" viewBox=\"0 -647.8 1000.5 793.3\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-labelledby=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\n<title id=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\\Rightarrow</title>\n<defs aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-21D2\" d=\"M580 514Q580 525 596 525Q601 525 604 525T609 525T613 524T615 523T617 520T619 517T622 512Q659 438 720 381T831 300T927 263Q944 258 944 250T935 239T898 228T840 204Q696 134 622 -12Q618 -21 615 -22T600 -24Q580 -24 580 -17Q580 -13 585 0Q620 69 671 123L681 133H70Q56 140 56 153Q56 168 72 173H725L735 181Q774 211 852 250Q851 251 834 259T789 283T735 319L725 327H72Q56 332 56 347Q56 360 70 367H681L671 377Q638 412 609 458T580 514Z\"></path>\n</defs>\n<g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-21D2\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use>\n</g>\n</svg>空地(火烧完树之后变为空地)</li>\n<li>空地<svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"2.324ex\" height=\"1.843ex\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.338ex;\" viewBox=\"0 -647.8 1000.5 793.3\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-labelledby=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\n<title id=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\\Rightarrow</title>\n<defs aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-21D2\" d=\"M580 514Q580 525 596 525Q601 525 604 525T609 525T613 524T615 523T617 520T619 517T622 512Q659 438 720 381T831 300T927 263Q944 258 944 250T935 239T898 228T840 204Q696 134 622 -12Q618 -21 615 -22T600 -24Q580 -24 580 -17Q580 -13 585 0Q620 69 671 123L681 133H70Q56 140 56 153Q56 168 72 173H725L735 181Q774 211 852 250Q851 251 834 259T789 283T735 319L725 327H72Q56 332 56 347Q56 360 70 367H681L671 377Q638 412 609 458T580 514Z\"></path>\n</defs>\n<g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-21D2\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"></use>\n</g>\n</svg>树(空地可能长出树)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210324093745190.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlbnl1c3VyYW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210324093758620.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlbnl1c3VyYW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>在以上规则中闪电和新生规则都涉及概率</p>\n<p>在以上的基础模型可以做出改进，可以将风向考虑进模型当中，那么在中心为火的情况下，下一时刻周围火势以及概率可以如下进行设置：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210324094546150.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlbnl1c3VyYW4=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>具体元胞自动机可以参考<a href='https://wenku.baidu.com/view/86050cb9aeaad1f347933f28.html'>链接</a></p>\n","text":"元胞自动机元胞自动机的构成：原版自动机由元胞、元胞空间、元胞邻居和元胞规则四部分组成； 元胞状态：在最简单的情况下，元胞有两种可能状态；较复杂情况下，具有多种状态，元胞的状态都按照元胞自动机的动力规则不断更新； 邻居：某一元胞状态更新是所要搜索的空间域就是该元胞的邻居；常见有夫诺...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数学建模","slug":"数学建模","count":5,"path":"api/categories/数学建模.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"模拟预测","slug":"模拟预测","count":1,"path":"api/tags/模拟预测.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%85%83%E8%83%9E%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%9C%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">元胞自动机</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Dominique Yiu","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/dominique-yiu/csdn/raw/master/theme/icon.png","link":"/","description":"There is only one heroism in the world, to see the world as it is and to love it. <br /> @ <b>realrealyiu@gmail.com</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Dominique-Yiu","twitter":"https://twitter.com/KingSwi39106371","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/whatever-36-86","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_49005782","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Softmax回归","uid":"d2d60baf6716ca9f3f193bfd072d2f20","slug":"Softmax回归","date":"2021-07-30T13:32:46.000Z","upda